==獎項==
基於BigWorld Technology開發的《戰車世界》，該遊戲的俄羅斯伺服器共91,311名玩家連線，此紀錄在2011年1月23號經過[[金氏世界紀錄|金氏世界紀錄]]的驗證，並列為「同一時間及MMO伺服器中最多線上玩家（Most Players Online Simultaneously on One MMO Server）」<ref name = "World of Tanks sets Guinness World Record">{{cite web |url=http://massively.joystiq.com/2011/02/24/world-of-tanks-sets-guinness-world-record/ |title=World of Tanks sets Guinness World Record |publisher=Joystiq |access-date=2014-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131225023606/http://massively.joystiq.com/2011/02/24/world-of-tanks-sets-guinness-world-record/ |archive-date=2013-12-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，2011年11月則再次刷新記錄到250,000線上玩家數。<ref name = "World of Tanks Sets a New Guinness World Record">{{cite web |url=http://news.mmosite.com/content/q/2011-12-09/world_of_tanks_sets_a_new_guinness_world_record.shtml |title=World of Tanks Sets a New Guinness World Record |publisher=MMOSite.com |access-date=2014-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103115223/http://news.mmosite.com/content/q/2011-12-09/world_of_tanks_sets_a_new_guinness_world_record.shtml |archive-date=2014-01-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

